        <detaileddescription>
<para>@bref prints the binary representation of an 8-bit unsigned integer.</para>
<para><parameterlist kind="param"><parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>val</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>The <computeroutput>val</computeroutput> [from 0 to 255]. The function prints the binary representation of this value by iterating over each bit. </para>
